data.description: Back on the market! Buyer got cold feet. ADORABLE 3 bedroom/1.5 bath move-in ready duplex on quiet street with UPGRADED LVP floors, replacement windows, brightly painted walls, FENCED-IN back yard, and rear OFF-STREET PARKING. Enter through the SUNLIGHT-FILLED living room with plenty of space for the essentials. The kitchen has tons of storage and a COZY eat-in area with room for more shelving. The rear mud room conveniently adjoins the combo half bath/laundry room. Up the CHARMING staircase you’ll find three BRIGHT bedrooms and full bathroom. Enjoy the ample closet space and unfinished basement for more STORAGE. RELAX on the front porch or take advantage of the beautiful weather on the rear patio. PRE-INSPECTED! The seller is willing to save the buyer the expense of home, termite, and radon inspections by sharing the ones that were completed within the past year (with a good offer). The duct work is in place to easily install central AC. Close to interstates, restaurants, and shopping. Don’t miss this one!
